data.description: Step inside this amazing hom, completely redone to make yours today! Large living & dining room in front offer plenty of space with new chandelier, family room overlooking backyard features a fireplace. The kitchen has freshly painted cabinets, new microwave , all stainless appliances and refrigerator. Huge pantry & laundry room. New wood laminate flooring throughout and all new paint. New privacy fence in backyard, Trex decking. Countless gorgeous Oak trees front and back! Big game room upstairs, with oversized split master retreat from the three additional bedrooms.
